data.description: This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home features many comforting amenities and added entertainment space. The foyer leads into the great room, a spacious room finished with vaulted ceilings and a gas fireplace. On the right side of the home there is 2 bedrooms with a jack and jill bath, each with their own closet. The right side of the home features the master suite. The room is incredibly spacious, and the bathroom is complete with a walk-in shower and bench, freestanding tub, double vanity sinks and more. The laundry can be found off the master suite, along with a kids nook. The dining area is on the back side of the great room and leads to an outdoor grilling porch with wide boxed beams. The dining and great room both open into the kitchen, which is complete with a walk-in pantry and large island with eating bar. There is a two car garage with double doors, and an upstairs optional bonus finish-out.All Materials shown are for conceptual purposes only. Buyer and buyers's agent must verify all data listed. Seller makes no representation that conceptual photos are actual of the coming soon homes. Please contact sellers directly for what will be included. Thank you.
